_2.png","line":11,"embedded":true},{"title":"csalchemsy_The_Lyceum_of_the_Astral_Chorus_on_the_Saint_Radia_aaa5bda5-d1a7-49ae-bfaf-16db572de122_3.png","target":"csalchemsy_The_Lyceum_of_the_Astral_Chorus_on_the_Saint_Radia_aaa5bda5-d1a7-49ae-bfaf-16db572de122_3.png","line":13,"embedded":true},{"title":"csalchemsy_The_Lyceum_of_the_Astral_Chorus_on_the_Saint_Radia_aaa5bda5-d1a7-49ae-bfaf-16db572de122_1.png","target":"csalchemsy_The_Lyceum_of_the_Astral_Chorus_on_the_Saint_Radia_aaa5bda5-d1a7-49ae-bfaf-16db572de122_1.png","line":15,"embedded":true},{"title":"csalchemsy_The_Lyceum_of_the_Astral_Chorus_on_the_Saint_Radia_fd35917b-d353-4951-9477-0fb66adfa269_2.png","target":"csalchemsy_The_Lyceum_of_the_Astral_Chorus_on_the_Saint_Radia_fd35917b-d353-4951-9477-0fb66adfa269_2.png","line":17,"embedded":true},{"title":"csalchemsy_The_Lyceum_of_the_Astral_Chorus_on_the_Saint_Radia_fd35917b-d353-4951-9477-0fb66adfa269_3.png","target":"csalchemsy_The_Lyceum_of_the_Astral_Chorus_on_the_Saint_Radia_fd35917b-d353-4951-9477-0fb66adfa269_3.png","line":19,"embedded":true},{"title":"csalchemsy_The_Lyceum_of_the_Astral_Chorus_on_the_Saint_Radia_fd35917b-d353-4951-9477-0fb66adfa269_1.png","target":"csalchemsy_The_Lyceum_of_the_Astral_Chorus_on_the_Saint_Radia_fd35917b-d353-4951-9477-0fb66adfa269_1.png","line":21,"embedded":true},{"title":"csalchemsy_The_Lyceum_of_the_Astral_Chorus_on_the_Saint_Radia_fd35917b-d353-4951-9477-0fb66adfa269_0.png\nThe **Astral Chorus** blends psychology, psychic empathy, and occult archetype studies into a school of astral science. They pioneer experiments into shared dreamwalking and archetypal resonance.  \n\n**Dormitory — The Lyceum**: circular chambers painted with murals of constellations and archetypal figures, doubling as meditation and dream-mapping spaces.  \n\n- **Occult Specialty:** *Empathic attunement* — members can bond willingly with beasts rather than bind them. This skill alone gives them disproportionate power.  \n- **Role in Academy:** Their empathetic research “softens” students, making them harder to indoctrinate. This puts them in Finch’s crosshairs.  \n- **Rivalry:** At odds with **Crimson Flame**, debating compassion vs domination as the true path to strength.  \n- **Uniform Accents:** Constellation-embroidered linings in ties, faint dream-halo around their crest when using gifts.  \n\n### Tools\n- [[DREAMLENS","target":"csalchemsy_The_Lyceum_of_the_Astral_Chorus_on_the_Saint_Radia_fd35917b-d353-4951-9477-0fb66adfa269_0.png\nThe **Astral Chorus** blends psychology, psychic empathy, and occult archetype studies into a school of astral science. They pioneer experiments into shared dreamwalking and archetypal resonance.  \n\n**Dormitory — The Lyceum**: circular chambers painted with murals of constellations and archetypal figures, doubling as meditation and dream-mapping spaces.  \n\n- **Occult Specialty:** *Empathic attunement* — members can bond willingly with beasts rather than bind them. This skill alone gives them disproportionate power.  \n- **Role in Academy:** Their empathetic research “softens” students, making them harder to indoctrinate. This puts them in Finch’s crosshairs.  \n- **Rivalry:** At odds with **Crimson Flame**, debating compassion vs domination as the true path to strength.  \n- **Uniform Accents:** Constellation-embroidered linings in ties, faint dream-halo around their crest when using gifts.  \n\n### Tools\n- [[DREAMLENS","line":23,"embedded":true},{"title":"AURORA_SIGIL","target":"AURORA_SIGIL","line":34},{"title":"Dreams_Oneiromancy_Arc","target":"Dreams_Oneiromancy_Arc","line":36}],"class_name":"SmartBlock","last_embed":{"hash":"8w9ch3","at":1774633475957}},
